strings.Value: "Hey! Where is food in the bag? Used to be a lot."
"You ate three times your weight today! Just what happens to all those rations you toss in your maw?"
"I, of course, am aware that goblins are famous for their unsatiable hunger... but I certainly wasn't aware that I'll have one of those beasts in my group and will suffer as a result!"
"Urgathoa would have been pleased with your gluttony. Would have â€” if you weren't Lamashtu scum."
"If you will keep eating like that, hunt for yourself. I am running out of arrows."
